# Controls:

# settings and resetings maze start and end points:

clicking on any point will turn it green - that will be the starting point of the maze generation and where the pathfinder will start from.
clicking any point again will set an end point, but if this is done before the maze generation it will have to be set again.

to reset the points - click "r"
to reset the grid - click "n"


# generating and solving the maze:
A starting point does not have to be set for the maze to be able to generate

to run Prim's algorithm - click "p"
to run Recursive Backtracking algorithm - click "m"

# Once the starting and ending point are set:
to run breadth-first search - click "b"
to run depth-first search - click "d"
